{"tid":665543,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"生得柒真係處處碰釘 好撚慘","createTime":"2018-05-15T04:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T10:56:46.000Z","uid":40867,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"94b345ddcca423b2534b9250cc378878dbb48eaf","tid":665543,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T04:59:41.000Z","msg":"話說係fb見到個廣告 封面有三條女<br />\n<br />\n咁 有對比之下 <br />\n一定有比較啦 <br />\n無可否認其中一個係柒左d嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過我都諗 <br />\n又唔係乜大公司大財團 <br />\n好難全部都靚女嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n咁我又唔係買女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見廣告內容都岩我 所以click入去啦<br />\n<br />\n我先上原圖 你就明我講乜<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/125447_815d2ad27267d6a8503a820ff82c2f4c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F125447_815d2ad27267d6a8503a820ff82c2f4c.png&h=0a5eb163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n入去見到..<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/125526_892cdb2781d7b20e5e01c606da17fd4a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F125526_892cdb2781d7b20e5e01c606da17fd4a.png&h=3cba3fbc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/15/125534_dce9d9cc524b691bf3f43a62b15e28f0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F15%2F125534_dce9d9cc524b691bf3f43a62b15e28f0.png&h=7127d82a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 條女直接比人cut撚左<br />\n佢出現嘅唯一原因就係構圖上豐富d<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入到內容 重點位就直接切剩個膊頭比佢<br />\n<br />\n嗚啊 有冇得再慘d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d6a831851b864a844572d27274eb46e626032d","tid":665543,"uid":11506,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬俾人cut走咗深深不忿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1286db5f045fba0b2f2ab2057d032208fd892ab0","tid":665543,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b42365fccaa531f4168927f2aa1e741ef5a9f957","tid":665543,"uid":179547,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:02:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得右邊靚過中間喎"},{"pid":"17890e1ce1bce7bef4555110c575ccf583d88fd2","tid":665543,"uid":72240,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"1286db5f045fba0b2f2ab2057d032208fd892ab0","tid":665543,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:01:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"無撚cut埋左？"},{"pid":"61e2a9197599c31c74f850b258872dcf2db8ebbf","tid":665543,"uid":40867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e7d6a831851b864a844572d27274eb46e626032d","tid":665543,"uid":11506,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"樓豬俾人cut走咗深深不忿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:02:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定係我啦"},{"pid":"2b497c25b7306811ea3d02e77cc7e2f9da77e96f","tid":665543,"uid":21423,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T05:03:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70874f11b96ce498ef345d79acd0e3696f